In Acumatica ERP, you can flexibly customize the user interface (in particular, main menu items and workspace links) all users will see to adjust it to the business processes of your organization. Your customization of the user interface will make it easier for users to find and begin working with required forms and reports, speeding document processing in the system. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_7c559681-3ec5-4f9d-8d35-6a7bbd4bbb7c] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#_4aba298d-11d3-4edd-9758-61b85961bc1a] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__con_User_Interface_Configuration|Customization of the UI] *[HelpRoot_Administration\CS__con_Interface_Style_Change|Interface Style of Acumatica ERP]
| [anchor|#_304d9c04-219c-445a-9c01-27652a8aa2b3] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Add_Configure_Workspace|To Add and Configure a Workspace] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Add_Form_to_Workspace_Menu|To Add a Link to a Workspace] *[HelpRoot_Administration\CS__how_To_Change_Default_Theme|To Change the Default Theme of Acumatica ERP] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Delete_Tile_from_Workspace_Menu|To Delete a Tile from a Workspace ] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Delete_Workspace|To Delete a Workspace] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Display_Hide_Forms_in_Workspace_Menu|To Display and Hide Forms in a Workspace] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Regroup_Items_In_Workspace_Menu|To Regroup Forms and Reports in a Workspace ] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Remove_Form_From_Workspace_Menu|To Remove a Form or Report from a Workspace ] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Rename_Workspace|To Rename a Workspace] *[HelpRoot_Administration\AS__how_Reset_Menu_Settings|To Reset Menu Settings]
